v2.2.9.1; Startup check fix
Fixed check mark not showing next to the "Run on Windows Startup" option.

v2.2.9; Updater & Bug fix
Added updater that automatically checks for new versions of Always PTT.
Fixed duplicate config file being created in certain conditions.
Changed compression method making Always PTT even smaller in size.

