Added "View Always PTT Releases on GitHub" to the "Help" submenu.
Added "View Always PTT Wiki on GitHub" to the "Help" submenu.
Added "Submit Bug Report or Feature Request" to the "Help" submenu.
Changed some code to prepare for future updates and features.
Updated License Agreement to reflect what GitHub shows.
